            <div class="cart-recommended-section">
                <h3 class="cart-section-title">함께 구매하면 혜택이 커지는 다품목 제품</h3>
                <div class="cart-product-scroll-wrapper">
                    <button class="cart-scroll-button prev" onclick="scrollCartProducts('multi', 'prev')">
                        <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
